    "r1": {
        "description": "The equipping character can gain the Remedy effect. When they possess 1/2/3 Remedy stacks, Max HP will increase by <color=#99FFFFFF>12%/24%/40%</color>. 1 stack may be gained when the following conditions are met: 1 stack for 25s when using an Elemental Skill; 1 stack for 25s when the value of a Bond of Life value increases; 1 stack for 20s for performing healing. Stacks can still be triggered when the equipping character is not on the field. Each stack's duration is counted independently. In addition, when 3 stacks are active, Elemental Burst CRIT Rate will be increased by <color=#99FFFFFF>28%</color>. This effect will be canceled 4s after falling under 3 stacks."
    },
